item_name: Yamaha NS PA150 Paket Speaker Home Theater
item_desc:
NS-PA150

Paket speaker Centre dan 4 Surround Speaker. Speaker berperforma tinggi dan ideal untuk film dan musik HD

Two 8cm (3-1/4”) cone woofers and 1.4cm (1/2”) balanced dome tweeter for distinct dialogue and clear vocals (Centre speaker)
8cm (3-1/4”) cone woofer and 1.4cm (1/2”) balanced dome tweeter for clean full-range sound (Surround speakers)
Dynamic reproduction of HD sources
Large-size, gold-plated screw terminals
Wall Mountable
